snippet: A Florida polo club founder was sentenced to 16 years in prison on Friday after a jury for a second time found him guilty of killing a recent college graduate in a collision while driving drunk late one night in Palm Beach County....

headline.print_headline: Florida Polo Magnate Gets 16 Years for Deadly Drunken Driving Crash
headline.main: Florida Polo Magnate Gets 16 Years for Deadly Drunken Driving Crash

lead_paragraph: A Florida polo club founder was sentenced to 16 years in prison on Friday after a jury for a second time found him guilty of killing a recent college graduate in a collision while driving drunk late one night in Palm Beach County.
